## 🗂️ Output Structure

After cloning, your output directory will contain:
```
output/
├── example_com/
│   ├── index.html          # Main page
│   ├── about/index.html    # Nested pages
│   ├── images/             # All images
│   ├── css/                # Stylesheets
│   ├── js/                 # JavaScript files
│   ├── manifest.json       # Clone metadata
│   └── README.txt          # Summary report
└── ...
```

